item.description:
Husky Tales - Episode 3: 2v1
SUBSCRIBE: http://www.YouTube.com/SaveAsAwesome Also Me: http://www.YouTube.com/HuskyStarcraft Episode 3 is finally here! We got a lot of feedback on how to improve the series after episode 2 and want to say THANK YOU for the continued support as well as the legitimate feedback. Things we've changed: 1) We have started to improve the overall sound of the show. There should be more sound effects, music, cleaner audio etc. Please let us know if this is noticeable. 2) Most of the episodes will now follow a long term plot from episode to episode. Rather than just a couple jokes here and there about StarCraft there will be a story you can follow. 3) The writing of the last episode wasnt the greatest so we've taken a little more time on the scripts. We have also laid out the next group of episodes to ensure we arent covering any plot holes from making them too quickly. Thanks!
